{"id": "1406786351470219346", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "type": 19, "author_id": "645758482305253422", "author_name": "duxadidus", "author_bot": false, "content": "As a recommendation, try to use Gluttony's passive. In exchange for an Orison, it increases your maximum health by 20% up to twice. This is important because the Furnace's limit is proportional to maximum health. And the more points you have in the Furnace, the more shield Salvador can use. Although you can also use those points directly to recover health.\n\nIn short, bigger is better <:cute1:1356053053568192717>", "timestamp": "2025-08-17T23:46:43.017000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["732651659360206870"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1406782236577235060", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
